\par A }{\i\fs20 remove disease }{\fs20 spell cast before the transformation is complete will restore an afflicted creature to normal. Afterward, however, only a }{\i\fs20 heal }{\fs20 or }{\i\fs20 mass heal }{\fs20 spell can reverse the affliction.
\par }{\b\fs20 Mucus Cloud (Ex):}{\fs20  An aboleth underwater surrounds itself with a viscous cloud of mucus roughly 1 foot thick. Any creature coming into contact with and inhaling t
